LEGIONNAIRE'S DISEASE EPIDEMIOLOGY (10)
=======================================
[Regarding urine antigen tests for Legionella:]
I believe that BINAX markets both an RIA (radioimmunoassay) and
EIA (enzyme immunoassay) [generally easier to perform - Mod.] kit
for urinary antigen detection of L. pneumophila serogroup 1.
